Fikile Mbalula to deal with the Deputy minister who slapped a woman&nbsp; Fikile Mbalula is looking forward to dealing with the man promoting women abuse. Fikile Mbalula is shocked as to how a well respected man of Manana's calibre could act like a wild animal. Mduduzi Manana is the Deputy minister of Education who slapped a woman publicly in women's month. Fikile Mbalula says that a lot people don't take the anti women abuse movement serious, but now the Deputy minister will be a very good example of what men who abuse woman face.